    <category term="動詞ない形" scheme="https://yabai.tw/tags/%E5%8B%95%E8%A9%9E%E3%81%AA%E3%81%84%E5%BD%A2/"/>
    
  </entry>
  
  <entry>
    <title>建立 Andriod Virtual Device</title>
    <link href="https://yabai.tw/androidstudio/general/avd/"/>
    <id>https://yabai.tw/androidstudio/general/avd/</id>
    <published>2024-03-05T08:17:24.000Z</published>
    <updated>2024-03-05T08:35:38.785Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>AVD 全名為 Android Virtual Device，為 Andriod 的模擬器，讓我們可測試不同 Andriod Device 與 API 版本。</p><a id="more"></a><h2 id="Version"><a href="#Version" class="headerlink" title="Version"></a>Version</h2><p>macOS Sonoma<br>Andriod Studio 2023.2.1</p><h2 id="Virtual-Device-Manager"><a href="#Virtual-Device-Manager" class="headerlink" title="Virtual Device Manager"></a>Virtual Device Manager</h2><p><img src="/images/androidstudio/general/avd/avd001.webp" alt="avd001"></p><p><em><strong>More Actions -&gt; Virtual Device Manager</strong></em></p><ul><li>使用 Virtual Device Manager 建立 AVD</li></ul><h2 id="Device-Manager"><a href="#Device-Manager" class="headerlink" title="Device Manager"></a>Device Manager</h2><p><img src="/images/androidstudio/general/avd/avd002.webp" alt="avd002"></p><ul><li>AVD 管理介面</li></ul><h2 id="Create-Vitual-Device"><a href="#Create-Vitual-Device" class="headerlink" title="Create Vitual Device"></a>Create Vitual Device</h2><p><img src="/images/androidstudio/general/avd/avd003.webp" alt="avd003"></p><ul><li><code>+</code>：建立 AVD</li></ul><h2 id="Select-Hardware"><a href="#Select-Hardware" class="headerlink" title="Select Hardware"></a>Select Hardware</h2><p><img src="/images/androidstudio/general/avd/avd004.webp" alt="avd004"></p><ul><li>選擇要模擬的硬體</li></ul><h2 id="System-Image"><a href="#System-Image" class="headerlink" title="System Image"></a>System Image</h2><p><img src="/images/androidstudio/general/avd/avd005.webp" alt="avd005"></p><ul><li>選擇要使用的 image</li></ul><h2 id="SDK-Component-Installer"><a href="#SDK-Component-Installer" class="headerlink" title="SDK Component Installer"></a>SDK Component Installer</h2><p><img src="/images/androidstudio/general/avd/avd006.webp" alt="avd006"></p><ul><li>下載 image</li></ul><p><img src="/images/androidstudio/general/avd/avd007.webp" alt="avd007"></p><ul><li>Image 下載完畢，按 <code>Next</code> 繼續</li></ul><h2 id="Andriod-Virtual-Device"><a href="#Andriod-Virtual-Device" class="headerlink" title="Andriod Virtual Device"></a>Andriod Virtual Device</h2><p><img src="/images/androidstudio/general/avd/avd008.webp" alt="avd008"></p><ul><li>可自訂 AVD 名稱，按 <code>Finish</code> 完成</li></ul><h2 id="Run-Device"><a href="#Run-Device" class="headerlink" title="Run Device"></a>Run Device</h2><p><img src="/images/androidstudio/general/avd/avd009.webp" alt="avd009"></p><ul><li><code>|&gt;</code>：執行 AVD</li></ul><p><img src="/images/androidstudio/general/avd/avd010.webp" alt="avd010"></p><ul><li>Andriod 模擬器順利執行在 macOS</li></ul><h2 id="Conclusion"><a href="#Conclusion" class="headerlink" title="Conclusion"></a>Conclusion</h2><ul><li>AVD 安裝過程尚稱平順，唯 Andrio Studio + AVD 同時開啟，記憶體已經接近 8GB，相當吃記憶體</li></ul><h2 id="Reference"><a href="#Reference" class="headerlink" title="Reference"></a>Reference</h2><ul><li><a href="https://developer.android.com/studio" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Android Studio</a>, <a href="https://developer.android.com/studio/run/managing-avds" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Create and manage virtual devices</a></li></ul>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;AVD 全名為 Android Virtual Device，為 Andriod 的模擬器，讓我們可測試不同 Andriod Device 與 API 版本。&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
    
